Added support for selecting the `tui_forms` renderer used by the wizard. The renderer can be set via the `config.renderer` field in `cookieplone-config.json` or via the `COOKIEPLONE_RENDERER` environment variable, which takes precedence. The `--no-input` flag still forces the `noinput` renderer. Invalid renderer names are reported with a clear error listing the available options. @ericof
